dct_title_s: Tabula geographica nova omnium oculis exibens et proponens verissimam descriptionem potentissimi et aurifen Regni Guiana
dct_alternative_sm: Neuwe Landtaffel, in welcher eigentlich, und warhafftiglich furgestelt wird, das gewaltige und goldtreiche Kunigreich Guiana so daligt under der aequinoctial Linien zwischer Brasilien und Peru
dct_description_sm: siti per nautam aliguem qui Gualthero Ralegh navigatione semper adsuit delineata.
Decorative cartouches, compass roses, rhumb lines.
Pictorial vignettes of figures (including woman and headless man with bow and arrows) and fauna.
Descriptive text in bottom left: Nota; and throughout.
Adapted from an earlier map by Jodocus Hondius.
Parallel title and descriptive text in German.
